snippet.textDisplay:
I just got tested today and I got positive for SARS-CoV-2. 

I was told to stay at home for 10 days and see for improvement been sick since 10/16 also been home ever since.

Now it’s 10/21 got tested yesterday 10/20. Therefore I will have to wait till 10/25 to get tested again.

Lost taste and sense of smell. Headaches (Mostly migraines) Tiredness. Heavy Eyes. Coughing. Mucus. Body Aches.
